    EditorSessionCommitInfoProcessingJob

    public abstract class CDOCommitInfoProcessingJob
extends org.eclipse.core.runtime.jobs.Job
    Job for processing whether a remote change affects the underlying component and the transaction. Also contains information about the detached CDO objects that should be removed explicitly from the editor page inputs.
